name: airlock
desc: A portal stocked with 4 EVA suits for entry and egress to the station.

name: door_bulkhead
desc: A light airtight doorway which can be closed, does not have any reinforcement and can be easily overridden.

name: door_security
desc: A medium weight airtight doorway which can be closed with advanced security to prevent tampering and make it difficult to break through.

name: door_blast
desc: A heavyweight airtight doorway which is sturdy enough to withstand ship weapons fire and almost impossible to breach by intruders.

name: dock_small
desc: A docking portal to accommodate small ships.

name: dock_medium
desc: A docking portal to accommodate medium ships.

name: dock_large
desc: A docking portal to accommodate large ships.

name: drydock_small
desc: Facilitates the repair and refitting of small-sized starships.

name: drydock_medium
desc: Facilitates the repair and refitting of medium-sized starships.

name: drydock_large
desc: Facilitates the repair and refitting of large-sized starships.

name: reactor_crystal_small
desc: Core reactors consume dense high-energy reactive crystals to generate power, however the crystals are rare and therefore costly. Core reactors can be used to boot-strap plasma fusion reactors which are more cost-efficient. Must be attached to an engineering station to operate.

name: reactor_crystal_medium
desc: Core reactors consume dense high-energy reactive crystals to generate power, however the crystals are rare and therefore costly. Core reactors can be used to boot-strap plasma fusion reactors which are more cost-efficient. Must be attached to an engineering station to operate.

name: reactor_crystal_large
desc: Core reactors consume dense high-energy reactive crystals to generate power, however the crystals are rare and therefore costly. Core reactors can be used to boot-strap plasma fusion reactors which are more cost-efficient. Must be attached to an engineering station to operate.

name: reactor_fusion_small
desc: Fusion reactors use a small amount of Basic Materials (in this case hydrogen and helium) in a plasma toroid to cause fusion of the simple atoms to generate large amounts of energy. A byproduct of this process results in a very small amount of intermediate materials.

name: reactor_fusion_medium
desc: Fusion reactors use a small amount of Basic Materials (in this case hydrogen and helium) in a plasma toroid to cause fusion of the simple atoms to generate large amounts of energy. A byproduct of this process results in a very small amount of intermediate materials.

name: reactor_fusion_large
desc: Fusion reactors use a small amount of Basic Materials (in this case hydrogen and helium) in a plasma toroid to cause fusion of the simple atoms to generate large amounts of energy. A byproduct of this process results in a very small amount of intermediate materials.

name: storage_xs
desc: Storage modules provide a place to store trade goods like materials and components for use in trade of production and construction.

name: storage_small
desc: Storage modules provide a place to store trade goods like materials and components for use in trade of production and construction.

name: storage_ms
desc: Storage modules provide a place to store trade goods like materials and components for use in trade of production and construction.

name: storage_ml
desc: Storage modules provide a place to store trade goods like materials and components for use in trade of production and construction.

name: storage_large
desc: Storage modules provide a place to store trade goods like materials and components for use in trade of production and construction.

name: station_security
desc: A small station for 1-4 Security personnel to be stationed at. Weapon power for Security personnel can be increased by attaching an Armory.

name: station_engineering
desc: A small station for 1 Engineer to be stationed at. Engineering stations are required for reactors and computing cores.

name: station_central_command
desc: An expanded central command center for the base commander and senior staff.

name: fabrication_structure_small
desc: A fabrication bay for scructural components. Turns Basic and Intermediate Materials into Construction Components.

name: fabrication_structure_large
desc: A fabrication bay for scructural components. Turns Basic and Intermediate Materials into Construction Components.

name: fabrication_basic_small
desc: A fabrication bay for Basic Components. Turns Basic Materials into Basic Components.

name: fabrication_basic_large
desc: A fabrication bay for Basic Components. Turns Basic Materials into Basic Components.

name: fabrication_inter_small
desc: A fabrication bay for Intermediate Components. Turns Intermediate Materials into Intermediate Components.

name: fabrication_inter_large
desc: A fabrication bay for Intermediate Components. Turns Intermediate Materials into Intermediate Components.

name: fabrication_adv_small
desc: A fabrication bay for Advanced Components. Turns Advanced Materials into Advanced Components.

name: fabrication_adv_large
desc: A fabrication bay for Advanced Components. Turns Advanced Materials into Advanced Components.

name: quarters_basic_small
desc: Basic quarters provide comfortable living quarters with basic food and entertainment needs.

name: quarters_basic_medium
desc: Basic quarters provide comfortable living quarters with basic food and entertainment needs.

name: quarters_basic_large
desc: Basic quarters provide comfortable living quarters with basic food and entertainment needs.

name: quarters_luxury_small
desc: Luxury quarters provide luxuriant living quarters with advanced food and entertainment needs.

name: quarters_luxury_medium
desc: Luxury quarters provide luxuriant living quarters with advanced food and entertainment needs.

name: quarters_luxury_large
desc: Luxury quarters provide luxuriant living quarters with advanced food and entertainment needs.

name: entertainment_rec_hall
desc: A large space dedicated to the entertainment of games and socializing.

name: entertainment_mess_hall
desc: Rudimentary dining area for staff and workers which provides for modest relaxation and socialization.

name: entertainment_theater
desc: A large space with many seats facing a stage for performance of music, dance and other important functions.

name: entertainment_casino
desc: Provides a floor for games of skill and chance which are highly entertaining but also highly addictive. Note that gambling is frowned upon by some cultures and some visitors may take offense to the presence of a casino.

name: entertainment_spa
desc: People enjoy the deep relaxation and pampered treatment at spas to relieve stress and find refreshment.

name: entertainment_pub
desc: Social establishments for the consumption of alcohol and light foods, can occasionally get rowdy or lead to security incidents.

name: entertainment_restaurant
desc: A much more elegant and relaxing venue for dining and socializing than the mess hall.

name: shop_small
desc: Shops provide opportunities for tourists and visitors to purchase manufactured goods such as tools, clothing and trinkets by which to remember your station.

name: shop_medium
desc: Shops provide opportunities for tourists and visitors to purchase manufactured goods such as tools, clothing and trinkets by which to remember your station.

name: shop_large

name: trade_center
desc: The trade center employs commerce experts and liaisons with traders to improve trade outcomes while also providing them with the best computing tools in order to conduct deep market analysis.

name: hydro_bay_small_square_glass
desc: Hydroponics bays can be used to grow necessary plant life for trade, research, relaxation or consumption by station staff. In addition each bay provides a small amount of life support.

name: life_support_small
desc: Life Support modules convert Basic Materials into breathable atmosphere and remove waste gases and contagions from the air to keep it fresh and clean, while also managing the heating and cooling of the air.

name: life_support_medium
